      <title>前中情局官员被指控帮助韩国购买奢侈品包</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ex-cia-official-accused-of-helping-south-korea-for-luxury-bags</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国检察官起诉了一位前中央情报局朝鲜问题分析师，指控他离开该机构后为韩国担任间谍，以换取奢侈品和其他礼物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-17/ex-cia-official-accused-of-helping-south-korea-for-luxury-bags</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 00:36:43 GMT</pubDate>
